# Personal Task Manager

A full-stack Personal Task Manager application that enables users to securely manage their daily tasks through a modern web interface. The project features JWT authentication, a FastAPI REST API, a Streamlit frontend, and PostgreSQL for persistent data storage. The application is fully containerized using Docker and deployed on Render.

---

## Live Demo

**Frontend:**
https://personal-task-manager-frontend-dkhf.onrender.com

**Backend API:**
https://personal-task-manager-zflc.onrender.com

**Swagger API Documentation:**
https://personal-task-manager-zflc.onrender.com/docs

**GitHub Repository:**
https://github.com/GAUTHAM-VK/PERSONAL_TASK_MANAGER
---

# Project Overview

The Personal Task Manager is designed to help users organize and manage their daily tasks efficiently.

Each registered user has a secure personal workspace where they can:

* Register a new account
* Log in securely
* Create tasks
* Update tasks
* Delete tasks
* Search tasks
* Filter tasks
* Track task completion
* View task summary statistics

The backend exposes REST APIs developed using FastAPI, while the frontend is built using Streamlit to provide an intuitive user interface.

---

# Features

### Authentication

* User Registration
* Secure Login
* JWT Authentication
* Password Hashing using bcrypt

### Task Management

* Create Tasks
* View Tasks
* Update Tasks
* Delete Tasks
* Mark Tasks as Completed

### Search & Filters

* Search by Title
* Search by Description
* Filter by Status
* Filter by Priority

### Dashboard

* Total Tasks
* Pending Tasks
* Completed Tasks

### Deployment

* Dockerized Backend
* Dockerized Frontend
* PostgreSQL Database
* Cloud Deployment using Render

