# System Architecture

```
                User
                  │
                  ▼
      Streamlit Frontend (Render)
                  │
            REST API Requests
                  │
                  ▼
       FastAPI Backend (Render)
                  │
                  ▼
      PostgreSQL Database (Render)
```

